	<item>
		<title>5 Tile Trends to Watch in 2025</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[marbure_admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>From large-format slabs to bold geometric patterns, 2025 is shaping up to be an exciting year for tile design. Here are the five trends our design team is seeing most in client showroom visits this year.</p><h2>1. Oversized Slabs</h2><p>600x1200mm and larger formats are becoming increasingly popular for both floors and walls, reducing grout lines for a sleek, seamless look.</p><h2>2. Warm Neutrals</h2><p>Beige, cream, and warm grey tones are replacing the cooler tones of recent years, bringing a sense of comfort and warmth to interiors.</p>]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[From large-format slabs to bold geometric patterns, here are the five tile design trends dominating 2025.]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
		<wp:post_name>tile-trends-2025</wp:post_name>
		<wp:status>publish</wp:status>
